    dc:identifier="http://www.notapathetic.com/comments/1395"
    dc:description="Sorry to my parents and Freaud but there is a MASSIVE generational wealth gap  in this country that has NOTHING to do with immigrants, crime or superstar footballers. Wealth is NOT filtering down through the generations..."
