	<dl>
	<dt>Sorry to my parents and Freaud but there...</dt>
	<dd><p>Sorry to my parents and Freaud but there is a MASSIVE generational wealth gap  in this country that has NOTHING to do with immigrants, crime or superstar footballers. Wealth is NOT filtering down through the generations,  even if I earn many times more money than my elders I am still so much poorer because of insane property prices. Presumably I should be happy that I will be in a position to screw my children in the same way later in my life. Unfortunately no party is addressing this. </p>
	<small>
	written 26th Apr 2005 <!--  | <a href="../email/1395">Email this
    to a friend</a> | <a
    href="/abuse/?postid=1395">abusive?</a> -->
	</small>
	</dd>
	</dl>

